Need to build repo rcs first

./configure --with-llvmsrc=`llvm-config --src-root` --with-llvmobj=`llvm-config --obj-root` --with-rcssrc=<rcs srouce directory> --with-rcsobj=<rcs object directory> --prefix=`llvm-config --prefix`
make
make install

Generate a bitcode file using clang 3.0
e.g. clang++ hello.cpp -o hello.bc -c -emit-llvm

Online mode
dynaa_insert_alias_checker.py hello.bc <aa> [--inline]
If --inline is specified, the output executable is hello.inlined; otherwise,
the output executable is hello.alias_checker.
Run the output executable. If it aborts or fails asserts, there is an error in
the alias analysis we are checking.

Offline mode
dynaa_hook_mem.py hello
./hello.inst
mv /tmp/pts hello.pts
dynaa_check_aa.py hello.bc hello.pts <aa>
